"```sql\nSELECT \n    (SUM(CASE WHEN Laboratory.Date LIKE '1981-11-%' THEN Laboratory.T-CHO END) - \n     SUM(CASE WHEN Laboratory.Date LIKE '1981-12-%' THEN Laboratory.T-CHO END)) / \n    NULLIF(SUM(CASE WHEN Laboratory.Date LIKE '1981-12-%' THEN Laboratory.T-CHO END), 0) AS decrease_rate\nFROM \n    Laboratory \nINNER JOIN \n    Patient ON Laboratory.ID = Patient.ID\nWHERE \n    Patient.Birthday = '1959-02-18';\n```"